OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,FA multi-faith football event has taken
OL,7,Fplace in the Lake District to bring
OL,8,Ftogether various religious groups.
OL,10,FThe match was hosted by Churches
OL,11,FTogether in Windermere and followed
OL,12,Fthe signing of the Westmorland and
OL,13,FFurness Faith Covenant on 1 July 2026.
OL,15,FAmy Bland, chaplain at Westmorland
OL,16,FGeneral Hospital, said: "It's great to
OL,17,Fmeet people in a fun and relaxed way,
OL,18,Fto chat about life and to play
OL,19,Ffootball together."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
