CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783700375
OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,FJonny Gios from Churches Together in
OL,7,Fthe county spoke about how pleased he
OL,8,Fis to see more peple of faith coming
OL,9,Fto Cumbria.
OL,11,FHe said: "Because you can share those
OL,12,Fvolunteers, those resources and also
OL,13,Fit says something about unity as well.
OL,14,FSo, for instance, the mosque at
OL,15,FDalton. I'm really pro the mosque
OL,16,Fcoming to Dalton-in-Furness.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783700375
OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,F"We need to support them as much as
OL,7,Fthey support us when we go through
OL,8,Fdifficult times. And it's really
OL,9,Fwonderful to see them coming into the
OL,10,Fcommunity."
OL,12,FZayaad Mohammed's daughters joined the
OL,13,Fpre-match kick about with a young
OL,14,FJewish girl. He says every faith can
OL,15,Fsustain on their own - but not thrive.
OL,17,F"So when I see my children playing
OL,18,Fwith other children of different
OL,19,Ffaiths, it reassures me that we're in
OL,20,Fthe right place," he said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
