PN,32904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783700375
OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,F"Cumbria has always been a warm and
OL,7,Fsecure space. As a muslim community,
OL,8,Fwe felt that as well, being here,
OL,9,Fsetting up and being welcomed as a
OL,10,Fcommunity to exist and thrive.
OL,12,F"So for me, there's no better place. I
OL,13,Fmean times of uncertainty and
OL,14,Fcomplexity, specifically around the
OL,15,Flast couple of years where there's
OL,16,Fbeen protests on immigration and other
OL,17,Ffaiths, we haven't had that.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783700375
OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,F"We've seen nothing but warmth and
OL,7,Fneighbourly kind of behaviour from all
OL,8,Fof our friends. So if you are finding
OL,9,Fyourself in a difficult space, reach
OL,10,Fout.
OL,12,F"Reach out to the church, the mosque,
OL,13,Fwe know that there's not a synagogue,
OL,14,Fand we're working to bring a synagogue
OL,15,Fto Cumbria. But don't feel these are
OL,16,Fspaces that you can't come into.
OL,17,FYou're more than welcome to."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
