CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783700375
OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,FThe match took place at the Lakes
OL,7,FSchool in Windermere and organiser
OL,8,FAbigail Mann highlighted the history
OL,9,Fof some of the participants.
OL,11,FShe said: "As part of this team today,
OL,12,Fwe have grandchildren of the
OL,13,FWindermere children. So they are the
OL,14,Fthird generation playing on behalf of
OL,15,Fthe Jewish community, and they are
OL,16,Fplaying alongside refugees who have
OL,17,Fjust arrived in Cumbria and are
OL,18,Frebuilding their lives."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
