PN,32907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783700375
OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,FJames Gordon, the grandson of one of
OL,7,Fthe child Holocaust survivors brought
OL,8,Fto the Lake District, was among those
OL,9,Fattending.
OL,11,FHe said: "After the Second World War,
OL,12,Fmy grandfather was flown here from
OL,13,FPrague, where he recuperated, found
OL,14,Fhope and built a new life.
OL,16,F"And to me, that's what's so special:
OL,17,Fan opportunity to do what my
OL,18,Fgrandfather did. He played in that
OL,19,Fgame with his friends against the
OL,20,Flocal community, and we come here
OL,21,Ftogether as a community today."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
