OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,FTrevor Friedman is the son of a
OL,7,FHolocaust survivor and he spoke about
OL,8,Fhis feelings regarding the current
OL,9,Fglobal situation.
OL,11,FHe said: "These are troubled times.
OL,12,FEven up here, we've had some degree of
OL,13,Fantisemitism. We have, the Windermere
OL,14,FLibrary, which has an exhibition to do
OL,15,Fwith the Windermere children, and
OL,16,Fthat's been subject to anti-Semitism
OL,17,Fand swastikas.
OL,26,@sD@JOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783700375
OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,F"And other communities as well. I have
OL,7,Fgood friends who are sikh, with this
OL,8,Frecent murder, they've had to tell
OL,9,Ftheir children to be careful when they
OL,10,Fgo out.
OL,12,F"So it's very sad that we have to talk
OL,13,Fabout these things, but all the more
OL,14,Freason for us to get together. Most of
OL,15,Fus just want to live happy lives,
OL,16,Ffamily, get on with our lives, enjoy
OL,17,Fthese things. We don't want to go out,
OL,18,Fyou know, causing trouble for other
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
