OL,3,CMulti-faith football event brings
OL,4,Creligions together in Cumbria
OL,6,F"People have misconceptions about what
OL,7,Fpeople believe or how they behave, and
OL,8,Fit's important we get the chance to
OL,9,Fchallenge those."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/10
